"  (doc authoring)    |                       |\n"
"                     V   (po4a executions)   >-----+--> translated\n"
"                     |                       |     |     documents\n"
" existing PO files -->--> updated PO files >-+     |\n"
"      ^                            |               |\n"
"      |                            V               |\n"
"      +----------<---------<-------+               ^\n"
"       (manual translation process)                |\n"
"                                                   |\n"
" addendum -->--------------------------------------+\n"
"\n"
